snippet.title: Flip Out Rush - Official Release Trailer
snippet.description:
The world of Flip Out Rush is waiting for you!
https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.grimkitty.flipoutrush

𝙀𝙣𝙙𝙡𝙚𝙨𝙨 𝙛𝙪𝙣 𝙞𝙨 𝙝𝙚𝙧𝙚!
Flip Out Rush is a classic styled endless runner game where the fun (and running) never stops! Rush, Jump, Collect Coins and flip your way through randomly generated levels to get the highest score possible!

𝙎𝙄𝙈𝙋𝙇𝙀 𝙂𝘼𝙈𝙀𝙋𝙇𝘼𝙔
Simple "One Tap" Gameplay was prioritized to make an easy accessible game for everyone to enjoy!

𝙀𝙉𝘿𝙇𝙀𝙎𝙎 𝘾𝙐𝙎𝙏𝙊𝙈𝙄𝙕𝘼𝙏𝙄𝙊𝙉
Spend the coins you collect while playing to purchase tons of customization options! From brand new Playable Characters, Backgrounds, and Grounds, the customization possibilities are endless!

𝙈𝙐𝙇𝙏𝙄𝙋𝙇𝙀 𝙇𝙀𝙑𝙀𝙇𝙎 𝙏𝙊 𝙋𝙇𝘼𝙔
Unlocking new grounds unlocks new levels! Each Ground acts differently, and has different level templates to generate. Unlock more to unlock more ways to play!

𝘼𝘾𝙃𝙄𝙀𝙑𝙀𝙈𝙀𝙉𝙏𝙎 𝘼𝙉𝘿 𝙈𝙊𝙍𝙀
Complete tasks to get Achievements and Rewards, Collect Daily Rewards to get new gifts everyday, Unlock Vaults using special Purple Coins, Play during events to get special Limited Edition Items, and find hidden secrets to immerse yourself into the world of Flip Out Rush!

--------------------------------------
Thanks so much for watching! Make sure to follow all of our socials to help keep up with the latest news at GRIMKITTY Productions!

Main Site: https://grimkittyproductions.wixsite.com/home
Insta: https://www.instagram.com/grimkitty_prod/
Twitter: https://twitter.com/GRIMKITTY_Prod
Gamejolt: https://gamejolt.com/@GRIMKITTYProductions
